  Translator: Burton Watson
By: Zhuangzi
Locus:
  Chapter: 1
  Paragraph: 15
Title: Free And Easy Wandering
---
I have no use for the rulership of the world! Though the cook may not
run his kitchen properly, the priest and the impersonator of the dead
at the sacrifice do not leap over the wine casks and sacrificial stands
and go take his place."
